scenes.description: The girls continue the zombie shooting game challenge.
Kobo Kanaeru appears on screen to announce the final scores of the test.
Vesta Zeta returns to the stage to announce her 2025 birthday commemorative goods.

subtitles.original: あー！
subtitles.english: Ahhh!

subtitles.original: ヤバいヤバい！
subtitles.english: This is bad, this is bad!

subtitles.original: あ、これまずい！閉じ込めてる！
subtitles.english: Ah, this is bad! It's closing in!

subtitles.original: これまずいよこれ！あー！やっちゃったやっちゃった！まずいよこれ！
subtitles.english: This is bad! Ahhh! I did it, I did it! This is bad!

subtitles.original: 今まつりちゃんが3秒で打ち抜いちゃったということは...
subtitles.english: Since Matsuri-chan just shot it down in 3 seconds...

subtitles.original: ...あの多分もう次ゾンビはこの動きしちゃいけないなっていうふうになって...
subtitles.english: ...the zombie probably realized it shouldn't move like that anymore...

subtitles.original: えー！やばい、学習するタイプだ！
subtitles.english: What?! Oh no, it's the type that learns!

subtitles.original: 学習しています！
subtitles.english: It's learning!

subtitles.original: 学習ゾンビなんだ！
subtitles.english: It's a learning zombie!

subtitles.original: ちょっと待って、じゃあ次ラプ様？先にやる？
subtitles.english: Wait a minute, so next is Lap-sama? Wanna go first?

subtitles.original: 先にやる？先にやる？
subtitles.english: Wanna go first? Wanna go first?

subtitles.original: やっぱ主役が最後でしょ！
subtitles.english: The star should go last, after all!

subtitles.original: Start!
subtitles.english: Start!

subtitles.original: わー！あー！
subtitles.english: Waaa! Ahhh!

subtitles.original: 当たるんかい！
subtitles.english: You're gonna hit me?!

subtitles.original: なんで当たんだよ！わー！
subtitles.english: Why did it hit?! Whoa!

subtitles.original: やばい、動きが激しいよでも！
subtitles.english: Oh no, but the movement is so intense!

subtitles.original: 撃て撃て撃て撃て！
subtitles.english: Shoot, shoot, shoot, shoot!

subtitles.original: 撃ちなさい！
subtitles.english: Shoot it!

subtitles.original: おお、当たるぞ当たるぞ！
subtitles.english: Oh, it's gonna hit, it's gonna hit!

subtitles.original: 頑張れ頑張れ、当たってるよ！
subtitles.english: Keep going, keep going, you're hitting it!

subtitles.original: 痛い痛い！そういうゲームだっけさ？！
subtitles.english: Ow, ow! Is that the kind of game this is?!

subtitles.original: Time's up!
subtitles.english: Time's up!

subtitles.original: やばいちょっと途中我慢できなかった...
subtitles.english: Oh no, I couldn't hold back halfway through...

subtitles.original: むかつきすぎて！
subtitles.english: Because it was so annoying!

subtitles.original: 最後の挑戦はゼータ！ 3, 2, 1, Go!
subtitles.english: The final challenger is Zeta! 3, 2, 1, Go!

subtitles.original: Start!
subtitles.english: Start!

subtitles.original: わー！うわー！
subtitles.english: Waaa! Whoa!

subtitles.original: めっちゃ動いてる、めっちゃ動いてるよ！
subtitles.english: It's moving a lot, it's moving a lot!

subtitles.original: あ、当たってる当たってる、当たってるよ！
subtitles.english: Ah, you're hitting it, you're hitting it!

subtitles.original: めっちゃ動いてるよー！
subtitles.english: It's moving so much!

subtitles.original: 回ってるから、めっちゃ回ってる！
subtitles.english: It's spinning, it's spinning like crazy!

subtitles.original: あと1枚、頑張れ！あと1枚！
subtitles.english: One more left, go for it! Just one more!

subtitles.original: あと1枚！当たんない！
subtitles.english: One more! I can't hit it!

subtitles.original: すごかった本当に！ゼータクリア！
subtitles.english: That was amazing, really! Zeta Clear!

subtitles.original: めちゃめちゃ軽かった、ゼータクリア！
subtitles.english: That looked so easy, Zeta Clear!

subtitles.original: ポイントは、2ポイントでした！わー！すごい！
subtitles.english: The score was... 2 points! Whoa! Amazing!

subtitles.original: みんなー！
subtitles.english: Guys!

subtitles.original: このテストで一番ポイントを取ったのは誰か、見てみようか？！
subtitles.english: Should we see who got the most points in this fest?!

subtitles.original: おー！え、めっちゃいい勝負！めっちゃいい！
subtitles.english: Whoa! Oh, it's a really close match! Really close!

subtitles.original: え、まつりが12点。はい。
subtitles.english: Eh, Matsuri is 12 points. Okay.

subtitles.original: で、トワちゃんが11点。はい。
subtitles.english: And Towa-chan is 11 points. Okay.

subtitles.original: で、ゼータが10点。はい。
subtitles.english: And Zeta is 10 points. Okay.

subtitles.original: そしてラプラスが... 14点！
subtitles.english: And La+ is... 14 points!
4 points! 4 points! 4 points!

subtitles.original: ラプラスが最下位ー！やっちゃったー！
subtitles.english: La+ is in last place! You blew it!

subtitles.original: 1位、1位、1位の方を選んでよ！
subtitles.english: Choose the first place, first place, first place one!

subtitles.original: すゴーい！おめでとー！
subtitles.english: Woooow! Congrats!

subtitles.original: みんな本当によく頑張ったね！
subtitles.english: You guys did very well!

subtitles.original: でも何より、みんな楽しんでくれて嬉しかった。
subtitles.english: And best of all, I'm glad everyone had fun.

subtitles.original: これからもっとエイム力を上げて、こぼみたいにうまくなれるといいね。
subtitles.english: I can't wait to see how much more you can improve your aiming skills in the future, like me.

subtitles.original: なになに、ちょっと待って、おい、おい！
subtitles.english: What, what, wait a minute, hey, hey!

subtitles.original: ちょっと......こっちが喋ってるんだけど？
subtitles.english: Um, I'm... I'm talking here.

subtitles.original: おい！こぼの話を聞いてよ！
subtitles.english: O! Listen to Kobo!

subtitles.original: やばい、怒られてるよ！やばい！
subtitles.english: Oh no, she's getting mad! Help!

subtitles.original: ま、とにかくゼータ！
subtitles.english: Anyway, Zeta!

subtitles.original: シークレット・エージェントになれるまでまだまだ遠〜い道のりだよ、いい？
subtitles.english: You still have a long, long way to go to become a full-fledged secret agent, okay?

subtitles.original: うん、勝負しよう！
subtitles.english: Yeah, let's have a match one day!

subtitles.original: バーイ！またね〜
subtitles.english: Bye! See ya~

subtitles.original: あ、あ、まだ、まだこっちだね！
subtitles.english: Ah, ah, wait, we're still over here!

subtitles.original: やばい、まつりちゃんもよ、どけどけどけ！
subtitles.english: Oh no, Matsuri-chan too, get out of the way!

subtitles.original: 今行くからね！
subtitles.english: I'm coming now!

subtitles.original: 逃げた逃げた！えー！
subtitles.english: She ran away, she ran away! Eh!

subtitles.original: That was such a crazy game! I got wet!
subtitles.english: That was such a crazy game! I got wet!

subtitles.original: From the water gun. They were shooting at me like crazy. I even had to change my clothes!
subtitles.english: From the water gun. They were shooting at me like crazy. I even had to change my clothes!

subtitles.original: But, I heard there's going to be announcements today. So, are you guys ready for the announcements?
subtitles.english: But, I heard there's going to be announcements today. So, are you guys ready for the announcements?

subtitles.original: A little ad break, yes.
subtitles.english: A little ad break, yes.

subtitles.original: では、告知です！お願いします！
subtitles.english: Now, for the announcements! Please!

subtitles.original: じゃじゃーん！ うわ、眩しい！
subtitles.english: Ta-da! Whoa, so bright!

subtitles.original: She's shining so bright. Oh my God, Zeta in an angelic outfit! Isn't that so cute?
subtitles.english: She's shining so bright. Oh my God, Zeta in an angelic outfit! Isn't that so cute?

subtitles.original: Angel costume! You guys have always said that you're scared of me, so you can't be scared of me now...
subtitles.english: Angel costume! You guys have always said that you're scared of me, so you can't be scared of me now...

subtitles.original: ...'cause I'm the most seiso person there is! So, Seiso Zeta! Seiso Zeta is here!
subtitles.english: ...'cause I'm the most seiso person there is! So, Seiso Zeta! Seiso Zeta is here!

subtitles.original: どう？可愛い？可愛いでしょ？ うん、真っ白だし。
subtitles.english: How is it? Cute? It's cute, right? Yeah, it's pure white.

subtitles.original: The costume looks so cute, right?
subtitles.english: The costume looks so cute, right?

subtitles.original: Kapan lagi bisa lihat Seiso Zeta ya guys ya? Berkostum, ber-cosplay sebagai angel-angel gitu.
subtitles.english: When else can you see Seiso Zeta, guys? Dressing up, cosplaying as an angel.

subtitles.original: Lucu? Iya iya Zeta lucu lucu.
subtitles.english: Cute? Yes, yes, Zeta is cute.

subtitles.original: Aku mau! Siapa yang mau? Aku aku!
subtitles.english: I want it! Who wants it? Me, me!

subtitles.original: But, we don't stop here because obviously there's going to be so many more items, and we're going to introduce them now.
subtitles.english: But, we don't stop here because obviously there's going to be so many more items, and we're going to introduce them now.

subtitles.original: じゃあ、こちらをご覧ください！どうぞ！
subtitles.english: Now, please take a look at these! Here!

subtitles.original: じゃじゃーん！ I'm better counting but that's probably six, right? Isn't that so awesome?
subtitles.english: Ta-da! I'm better at counting but that's probably six, right? Isn't that so awesome?
